After requesting a Amazon Data Download I found the folder stats&quot; folder Devices.Kindle.FreeTime.zip  (the account had a Kindle HD tablet) inside it are logs on kids. 
Doing a grep search across the entire directory of all downloads returns<p>&quot;log_timestamp&quot;,
